data.title: Movies Given the Green Light Online Trivia
data.meta_description: Each of the following films contains the word Green in its title. But do you know who was the star in each of these movies?
data.text: QuestionsChoices 1. How Green Was My Valley (1941) Patrick Swayze 2. Fried Green Tomatoes (1991) John Wayne 3. The Green Hornet (2011) Kathy Bates 4. The Corn Is Green (1945) Seth Rogen 5. The Green Mile (1999) Charlton Heston 6. The Odd Life of Timothy Green (2012) Jennifer Garner 7. Soylent Green (1973) Basil Rathbone 8. The Woman in Green (1945) Bette Davis 9. Green Dragon (2001) Maureen O'Hara
